  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a observational study aims to assess anal and genital human papillomavirus (HPV)
      infection status among men who have sex with men (MSM) in China, and their knowledge and
      attitude about HPV vaccine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
